title: Americas Funniest Videos - Nincompoops & Boneheads (2006)
description:
Product Description

Since its 1990 debut, ABC&#039;s long-running reality-television series, AMERICA&#039;S HOME VIDEOS, has served up hilarious homemade video clips of bloopers, pranks, and mishaps made by the eccentric characters that populate the American landscape. NINCOMPOOPS AND BONEHEADS presents a collection of clips showcasing intrepid souls both brave and stupid enough to attempt especially dangerous stunts like riding grocery carts down a grassy hillside.
